{"word":"ἀμελέω","slug":"ἀμελέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀμελέω</el></b> [<el>ἀ-</el><a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ priv.\">priv.</a>, <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μέλω\">μέλω</a></el> ‘care for’, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in 3 <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sg.\">sg.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μέλει\">μέλει</a></el>] <b><i>not to care:</i></b> <i>show no interest</i> <i>(in), pay</i> <i>no attention (to), ignore, disregard</i> <b><a href='B:470 22:5'>Mt 22:5</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><a href='B:610 4:14'>1 Ti 4:14</a>; <a href='B:650 2:3'>Hb 2:3</a>; <a href='B:650 8:9'>8:9</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> inf<b>. <a href='B:680 1:12'>2 Pt 1:12</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> In some of these passages <i>neglect</i> expresses the nuance emerg-ing from the context. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀμείνων\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἄμεμπτος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}